Package org.keycloak.protocol.oid4vc.issuance

Class VCIssuanceContext

java.lang.Object
org.keycloak.protocol.oid4vc.issuance.VCIssuanceContext
public class VCIssuanceContext extends Object
Holds the verifiable credential to sign and additional context information. Helps keeps the VerifiableCredential as clean pojo. Without any risk to mistakenly serialize unwanted information.
Author:
Francis Pouatcha
